text: Guns of the Black Witch () is a 1961 Italian French adventure movie directed by Domenico Paolella and starring Don Megowan, Silvana Pampanini, Germano Longo, Emma Danieli, Livio Lorenzon. ==Other websites== * Category:1961 adventure movies Category:Italian adventure movies Category:French adventure movies Category:Movies directed by Domenico Paolella
title: Guns of the Black Witch
